How this works

1 Wheel = 1 trip

1. 1 - Excited Rider
2. 10 Wheels -  Happy Commuter
3. 30 Wheels -  Safety Officer
4. 60 Wheels - Railroad Engineer
5. 90 Wheels - Master Conductor status
Every 30 ride = 6 free ride 
*Starting after first status - sponsor rewards apply.
*Resets every 3 months.

New Badges for every “season”

